snippet.title: Introducing "Vektor Z", A Fast & Furious Space Action Game, From ZaxtorGameS, Coming January 2022!
snippet.description:
My upcoming game "Vektor Z" can be found on Steam right HERE:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1855190/Vektor_Z/

Thank You for being here and watching!  I make content to help, entertain, and enlighten people.  With my indie game reviews, I could show you terrible Steam games I do not recommend, or in contrast show you little undiscovered indie gems I believe deserve your attention.  I also make inspirational videos, how-to videos, and even videos supporting you through a devastating heart break!  

If you want to support me, there are many ways to do that, but spending money isn't required.  You can support me big-time by simply watching my videos, give my videos that you enjoy comments and likes, or by linking my channel on your favorite online social media hang out!

*****************************************************
DONATING TO SUPPORT ME AND MY SON:
Being a divorced father raising my son on a single income isn't easy, so any and all donations are greatly appreciated!  

Want to show me your love?  Every dollar helps! 
My LiveStream Donation Link: https://youtube.streamlabs.com/Zaxtor99

Want to give me $10 in credit for food at DoorDash while you get $30 off DoorDash food delivered right to your front door as well? ($10 off your first 3 orders)
Please use this referral link!      https://drd.sh/qTDdyvNEttJOpD3C

Interested in trying HelloFresh easy-to-make healthy meals sent right to your home?
Use my promotional link and you'll get $100 off your first order and also give me a $10 credit on my weekly meals I am loving!  Use this link:
https://www.hellofresh.com/pages/share?c=HS-L4JL9YY90&utm_campaign=clipboard&utm_couponvalue=100&utm_invitername=Zachary&utm_medium=referral&utm_source=raf-share

***********************************
